      "text": "From an external sender pinging Incotin to the reply going back out — with triage, CRM logging, and a pt-PT draft in Renato's\nvoice all happening through Cowork.",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
