      "updated": 1779226431904,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Cowork sees every inbound across every channel and routes it into one CRM. Renato never opens Airtable directly — he reads, approves, and sends inside\nCowork.",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Cowork sees every inbound across every channel and routes it into one CRM. Renato never opens Airtable directly — he reads, approves, and sends inside\nCowork.",
